Mandala m = Create Mandala

Foreach i=1.0 To 6.0:

  Number x = i * 10.0

  Shape s = Create Shape:
    Geo triangle 
    Size x
    Color red 
    Rotation 0.0

  Number y = i * 20.0

  Layer l = Create Layer:
    Radius y 
    Shape s 
    Count 4 
    Offset 0.0 
    AngularShift 1

  addTo: (m, l)

draw: (m)
